13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 26 O.S. 2021, Section 8-105, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 8-105. A. When a tie vote is certified in the
17 nomination or election of any candidate in any Runoff Primary,
18 General Election, or any Primary Election, a second vote shall be
19 set for the next practicable election date listed in subsection B of
20 Section 3-101 of this title. When a second vote has occurred for a
21 Primary or a Runoff Primary election, the General Election for that
22 office shall move to the next practicable election date listed in
23 subsection B of Section 3-101 of this title.
