11 5. The meeting shall be held on a weekday, holidays excepted,
12 between the hours of 7:00 a.m. and 7:00 p.m.
13 C. D. When there are three (3) or more candidates and a tie for
14 first place occurs for the nomination of a candidate at a Primary
15 Election for which a Runoff Primary will be held, the names of the
16 tied candidates shall be placed on the Runoff Primary ballot.
17 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
